5:["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L17",null,{"value":[{"value":"예시","id":"예시","depth":2},{"value":"Props","id":"props","depth":2},{"value":"코드","id":"코드","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L18",null,{}],["$","$L19",null,{"metadata":"$2:props:children:props:children:2:props:pageMap:4:children:9:frontMatter","bottomContent":"$undefined","sourceCode":"# Text\n\n토큰 기반 타이포그래피 컴포넌트입니다. `as`로 렌더링할 HTML 요소를 지정할 수 있습니다.\n\n## 예시\n\n<ComponentPreview>\n  <TextDemo />\n</ComponentPreview>\n\n## Props\n\n| Prop     | Type     | Default   | 설명 |\n| -------- | -------- | --------- | ---- |\n| as       | `\"h1\"` \\| `\"h2\"` \\| … \\| `\"p\"` \\| `\"span\"` \\| `\"div\"` \\| `\"label\"` 등 | `\"p\"` | 렌더링할 요소 |\n| size     | Font size token (xsmall, small, medium, large, xlarge, display-*) | `\"medium\"` | 글자 크기 |\n| weight   | `\"regular\"` \\| `\"medium\"` \\| `\"semibold\"` \\| `\"bold\"` | `\"regular\"` | 굵기 |\n| intent   | ColorIntent \\| `\"inherit\"` | `\"inherit\"` | 텍스트 색상 의도 |\n| align    | `\"left\"` \\| `\"center\"` \\| `\"right\"` | `\"left\"` | 정렬 |\n| truncate | `boolean` | `false` | 말줄임 적용 |\n\n## 코드\n\n```tsx\nimport { Text } from \"pine-design-system\";\n\n<Text as=\"h2\" size=\"large\" weight=\"bold\">Heading</Text>\n<Text intent=\"neutral\">Body text</Text>\n```","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"id":"$undefined","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["Text","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["토큰 기반 타이포그래피 컴포넌트입니다. ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"as"}],"로 렌더링할 HTML 요소를 지정할 수 있습니다."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"예시","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10